<p rend="chapter">Ekaṭhānikādiyamakagāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="101"><hi rend="paranum">101</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Ākaṅkhakkhākaṅkhaṅga kaṅkhāgaṅgākhāgahaka,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Kaṅkhāgāhakakaṅkhāgha hā hā kaṅkhā kahaṃ kahaṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="102"><hi rend="paranum">102</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Appagabbho apagabbho amoho mā pamohako,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Maggamukhaṃ mokhamāha māhā mohamūhakkhamaṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="103"><hi rend="paranum">103</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Pāpāpāpabhavaṃ passaṃ pāpāpabhavuggato,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Pāpāpāpabhavāsaṅgā pāpāpāpabhavāgato.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="104"><hi rend="paranum">104</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Kusalākusalaṃ passaṃ kusalākusalaṃ caji,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Kusalākusalāsaṅga kusalākusalā cuto.</p>
